title: Monday Monkey Riot - Primal Primates
description:
DOWNLOAD THE EP

\"Dont be bugging dude, just give up love for the crew
Cause i know you hum our tunes like a didgeridoo
No limits, no rules, the old school bringin the news\"
(fonky Bomb)

Monday Monkey Riot are finally ready to introduce the sound of urban junglefunk hiphop under the watchful eyes of grandmaster Holy Father Bobby Ape!

The soundtrack to your riot, blockparty or quiet night at home with your loved ones...and your shotgun.
Prime Skitz and Shizzywigg has teamed up again, as a duo this time and are moving new tunes under a new name into a new era. So make your parents proud, submit your soul into the hands of Bobby Ape, join his army of loyal primate misfits and get down and dirty to the music that runs in the sewers of his domain.

Enjoy.....
Shizzywigg, a prophet in his service,
Prime Skitz, mixmaster extraordinaire
